", " Envy poisons my thoughts, coveting others' success.", ' Jealousy poisons my thoughts, resentment brewing within.', ' Bitterness festering like a venomous vine, entwining the soul in a web of resentment, poisoning the garden of peace. ", 'Bitterness like a poison, seeping into every crevice of the wounded heart. ']
